Chapter 7 - For Whom The Bell Tolls --
In this final episode, Ami Mercury makes a major blunder and spills a glass of water on Mistress Paige. After making a valiant apologetic effort to make things right, Ami Is instructed to undress and face her punishment. Master Doc starts things off with applying labia clamps and a large bell to her. While Mistress Paige rings the bell, Master Doc subjects Ami to a harsh caning that really gets her attention. The punishment is finished off with a good paddling, after which Paige treats Ami to a hot lesbian sex session!
title: Turning The Paige: Chapter Seven
